4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper's use of gradient descent methods and control laws can be seen as a form of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.DS (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper's discussion of decentralized control laws and interactions between neighboring agents can be seen as distributed computing.
